    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice.No one does stew like Peru. For your take on aji de gallina, you'll simmer chicken in a charred pepper sauce with walnut, chilli and cheese. Stew till fragrant and serve with fluffy white rice on the side for a hearty dinner.",
